                    About <span class="primary-color">CaseWise</span>
                </h2>
                
                <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        CaseWise was founded with a simple yet powerful vision: to democratize legal knowledge and empower individuals to understand the law on their own terms. Born from the frustration of legal complexity and inaccessibility, our team of legal experts and technology innovators came together to create a platform that transforms how people interact with legal information. We believe that knowledge is the ultimate equalizer, and everyone deserves access to clear, comprehensive legal resources regardless of their background or experience level.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p>
                        At our core, CaseWise is driven by the mission to empower individuals, promote legal literacy, and foster a society where people can confidently advocate for themselves. We are committed to breaking down barriers to legal understanding, providing tools that make complex concepts accessible, and building a community where everyone feels equipped to navigate the legal landscape. Our values of transparency, accessibility, and empowerment guide every feature we develop and every resource we provide. We're not just building a platform; we're building a movement toward legal empowerment for all.
                    </p>
                </div>
